Class BaseAtlasModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.atlasmap.core.BaseAtlasModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtlasModuleMXBean, AtlasModule
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CsvModule, JavaModule, JsonModule, KafkaConnectModule, PropertyModule, XmlModule
    public abstract class BaseAtlasModule
extends Object
implements AtlasModule, AtlasModuleMXBean
    The base implementation of the AtlasModule which implements common routines.
